  # UniOpBench
  
  CUDA 算子标准化基准测试数据集。每个算子提供 CUDA、Torch 实现及标准化测试。
  
  ## 目录结构
  
  ```
  UniOpBench/
  ├── operators/
  │   ├── elementary/    # add, sub, sin, sign
  │   ├── activation/    # relu, gelu, sigmoid
  │   ├── reduction/     # sum, mean, max, min, softmax
  │   ├── matmul/        # gemm, gemv, bmm, dense
  │   ├── attention/     # mha, gqa
  │   ├── conv/          # conv1d, conv2d, depthwiseconv
  │   ├── pool/          # avgpool, maxpool, minpool, sumpool
  │   ├── norm/          # batchnorm, layernorm, instancenorm, rmsnorm
  │   └── other/         # transpose, concat, scatter, gather, deformable, gatemlp
  ├── optest/            # 测试框架
  └── requirements.txt
  ```
  
  每个算子目录：
  
  ```
  operators/{category}/{operator_name}/
  ├── cases.yaml          # 测试参数配置
  ├── cuda_/kernel.cu     # CUDA 实现
  ├── torch_/ref.py       # PyTorch 参考
  ├── triton_/kernel.py   # Triton 实现
  └── test.py             # 统一测试入口
  ```
  
  ## 环境配置
  
  Python >= 3.10.0
  
  ```bash
  python -m venv && source .venv/bin/activate
  pip install -r requirements.txt
  pip install -e .
  ```
  
  ## 测试
  
  ```bash
  cd operators/{category}/{operator_name}
  
  # 单次测试
  python test.py --compile-only    # 仅编译
  python test.py --no-perf         # 跳过性能测试
  
  # 变体测试（从 cases.yaml 批量运行）
  python test.py --variants yaml
  ```
  
  ## 框架架构
  
  - `optest/core/` - Backend 抽象、TestCase、VariantGenerator、TestSuite
  - `optest/execution/` - 编译、运行、基准测试
  - `optest/reporting/` - 结果输出
