     - Processes 4 levels with different spatial resolutions (32x32, 16x16, 8x8, 4x4)
     - Uses grid-stride parallelization for efficient computation
     - Each thread computes one output element across all levels and sampling points
  
  2. **`MultiScaleDeformableAttention.py`**: PyTorch reference implementation
